{"tid":394883,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"粉絲鼓勵同古天樂拍拖 洋腸達人宣萱：做朋友咪幾好","createTime":"2017-09-10T10:47:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-12T15:35:21.000Z","uid":35964,"like":2,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"1b2d1a0ac8943eb8e84366b58dc9b458d306405d","tid":394883,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:47:41.000Z","msg":"宣萱及袁文傑擔任商場開幕嘉賓，二人再次化身Mall姐及游生亮相。宣萱提到前年開始自己接工作，自《不懂撒嬌的女人》播出後工作量大增，坦言有點應付不來。她透露即將跟古天樂旗下經理人公司合作，與多年前曾於無線合作過的Ronnie再度拍檔，宣萱說：「都係part-time合作形式，試下先，唔係簽約。」她坦言偏向拍劇，但現在的她會顧及生活，需要時間陪伴朋友及家人。她透露跟Ronnie將於下個禮拜開始合作，談到可有新工作方案可透露？她說：「唔講得！（《尋秦記》電影？）你問佢（古天樂）啦！」<br />\n<br />\n問到若有機會可會參演《尋秦記》電影版？宣萱坦言可以，她笑說：「其實從《刑事偵緝檔案》Fans已經有遺憾，因為結局我哋係分咗手。甚至有Fans訊息我，話我又無拍拖，古生又無拍拖，不如拍拖。（唔試吓？）依家做朋友咪幾好！」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/uptow/i4/d4945f375a9c10a5c073ed9043702fc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fuptow%2Fi4%2Fd4945f375a9c10a5c073ed9043702fc8.jpg&h=01a591d2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"bfb53f75c83521e1a4b8d093d8d0463a363b962c","tid":394883,"uid":16996,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:54:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://i.imgur.com/5TTqm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F5TTqm.jpg&h=7c1f6d0b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a7551c2341756ec03e3d072f167d3ea118f9b755","tid":394883,"uid":8048,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T10:56:06.000Z","msg":"洋腸達人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dcc0439ac8fe04550a6820b26cf9bed485204894","tid":394883,"uid":135767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T11:01:52.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"816930c8fdc95802e1bdee10ac7a391ef451e6df","tid":394883,"uid":130394,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-10T11:04:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"> 闊過紅隧 </span>"},{"pid":"75f9a9258855f4af81b11bc7f8ebc5aff24401f4","tid":394883,"u